title: Static Analysis

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATIO.description: Access coarse location sources, such as the mobile network database, to determine an approximate phone location, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine approximately where you are.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_BACKGROUND_LOC.description: Allows an app to access location in the background. If you're requesting this permission, you must also request either

android.permission.BLUETOOTH.description: Allows an application to view configuration of the local Bluetooth phone and to make and accept connections with paired devices.

android.permission.BLUETOOTH_ADMIN.description: Allows an application to configure the local Bluetooth phone and to discover and pair with remote devices.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.CHANGE_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to change the state of network connectivity.

android.permission.CHANGE_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to connect to and disconnect from Wi-Fi access points and to make changes to configured Wi-Fi networks.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

manifest_analysis.desc: A Service is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. "detail_basic_info_coke_freestyle_description" : "Satisfy your thirst with one day of unlimited Coca-Cola Freestyle® soft drinks at all participating Coca-Cola Freestyle® locations. Valid at Universal Studios Florida®, Universal's Islands of Adventure® and Universals Volcano Bay®.
"

"detail_basic_info_express_pass_line_description" : "Skip the regular lines with the Universal Express™ ticket.

It includes all-day admission to the Park, plus one-time express access to each ride and attraction and priority seating at select shows.*

This feature is popular among guests, so pre-purchase to guarantee Universal Express™ privileges.

*Does not apply to food and retail locations or non-seated shows."

"detail_basic_info_express_pass_restrictions_description" : "Paid theme park admission required. Limit one (1) express ride access entry per participating attractions using the Universal Express℠ queue. Valid at participating attractions.  Universal Express℠ passes available during normal theme park operating hours only. Not valid for separately ticketed special events. Additional restrictions may apply and benefits are subject to change without notice."

"detail_basic_info_food_allergy_line_description" : "At Universal Orlando™ Resort, we know it can be a challenge to dine out when you or someone you’re with has food allergies and/or intolerances. That’s why we offer a number of dining locations throughout Universal’s Islands of Adventure™, Universal Studios Florida™, Universal Studio’s Volcano Bay™, Universal CityWalk™ and our hotels where our chefs and culinary staff can accommodate your dietary needs related to common food allergies, phenylketonuria (PKU), metabolic disorders, and guests with multiple allergies/intolerances. 

Guests with questions about the dietary requests listed above and questions not answered here can contact us. Please call at least 14 days in advance. Our dining locations will do their best to accommodate guests with food allergies, but cannot guarantee that they will be able to meet all requests. 

If you aren’t able to research dining options ahead of time, don’t worry. You can ask to speak to a chef or manager at any restaurant within Universal Orlando Resort™ once you’re here. Let them know which guest in your party has a food allergy or intolerance, and what the allergy/intolerance is. Our culinary staff will make every effort to prevent that allergen from coming in contact with any part of that guest’s meal."

"detail_basic_info_package_pickup_description" : "Try complimentary Package Pick-Up at select merchandise locations within Universal Studios Florida® or Universal's Islands of Adventure® and your purchases will be sent to the front of the park to be picked up at your convenience.

All purchases are available to be picked up 3 hours after the time of purchase.

Purchases made in Universal Studios Florida may be picked up at It's A Wrap. Purchases made in Islands of Adventure may be picked up at Ocean Trader Market®.

If you are staying at Loews Portofino Bay Hotel, Hard Rock Hotel®, or Loews Royal Pacific Resort, your packages are delivered directly to your room. Packages are delivered to rooms the following day after 9 am. Guests staying at Universal's Cabana Bay Beach Resort may pick up their packages at the front desk the following day after 9 am."
"detail_basic_info_package_pickup_title" : "Want to buy something now but don’t want to carry it around all day?"

"vacation_planner_faq_item_1_message" : "You may pick up tickets at the Will Call Kiosk, where you will swipe the credit card used during purchase (for verification purposes only), enter the Reservation Number provided on this email receipt, and your tickets will print automatically. Your reservation number contains only the number 0 (zero) and never the letter O when entering it at the kiosk.

Florida Resident and/or Blue Man Group tickets must be picked up at a Pass Sales Booth at the front of either park by presenting your reservation number and a valid photo ID."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_1_title" : "Where do I pick up my theme park tickets?"

"vacation_planner_faq_item_2_message" : "Reservations included in your vacation package are included in your E-Travel Document. You must print a copy of the voucher within the E-Travel Document and present it for redemption, along with a valid Photo ID."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_2_title" : "Where do I retrieve my reservation voucher?"
"vacation_planner_faq_item_3_message" : "Early Park Admission begins one hour before the scheduled park opening. Be sure to bring your admission tickets and e-travel documents with you."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_3_title" : "What time can I enter the park with Early Park Admission?"

"vacation_planner_faq_item_4_message" : "Scheduled theme park transportation provided is based on regular park operating hours* (does not run continuously) to UNIVERSAL ORLANDO® theme parks. Seating/standing space is limited and on a first come, first served basis. *Not valid for Special Events, Groups or Early Park Admission."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_4_title" : "Is there FREE transportation from my hotel to the theme parks?"

"vacation_planner_faq_item_5_message" : "Guests wishing to take advantage of the Early Park Admission departures must call the UPRV Early Park Admission shuttle reservation line at 800-711-0080, between the hours of 8:00am and 8:00pm no later than one day prior to the day they wish to use Early Park Admission. This special charter service books by reservation ONLY, boarding passes will NOT be issued. Limited hotel participation available."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_5_title" : "How do I book the UPRV Early Park Admission shuttle?"

"vacation_planner_faq_item_6_message" : "Traffic delays of 15 to 20 minutes around the International Drive corridor and the Theme Parks are to be expected. If the transportation is delayed later than 20 minutes, please visit the hotel Front Desk or the Attraction Ticket Center located in the hotel lobby."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_6_title" : "What if the scheduled theme park transportation is late?"

"vacation_planner_faq_item_7_message" : "This theme park privilege is valid from park opening on the day of your check-in through park closing on your check-out day. If you arrive at our resort prior to check-in time, your hotel will check your bags and issue temporary room keys so that you can start enjoying your express access. On your check-out day, your room keys will be deactivated for hotel use, but you can continue to use your unlimited Express Pass through park closing. Please be advised that express access is only valid at participating attractions. Lastly, please note that these privileges do not apply to separately-ticketed special events such as Rock the Universe and Halloween Horror Nights.

At the express kiosks, you will be prompted to insert your room key card and follow the on screen instructions to print your Unlimited Express Pass. The kiosk will take a photo of you to print on the Express Pass. Show this pass at each express attraction entrance for free access throughout both theme parks. If you ever lose this Express Pass, please visit any of our Guest Services locations for assistance."
"vacation_planner_faq_item_7_title" : "I’m staying at a Universal Premier hotel. How do I receive my free Universal Express Unlimited Pass?"
"vacation_planner_faq_item_8_message" : "You can reach one of our agents Monday – Saturday, 7:30am - 10:00pm and Sunday, 7:30am – 9:00pm by calling 800.407.4275"

playstore_details.title: Universal Hollywood™ App
playstore_details.description:
Put everything you need to know about your trip to Universal Studios Hollywood in the palm of your hand. Download the official Theme Park app for free!
 It’s the easy way to:
•	Purchase select single and multi-day Theme Park tickets in the app.
•	Check ride, show and attraction wait times at home, on the go or in the park.
•	Customize your park experience using the itinerary, filtered lists and the map to plan your day.
•	Set ride wait time and show time alerts to make the most of your time in the park. 
•	Stay up-to-date with in-park notifications and news about upcoming special events.
•	Share your Universal Studios Hollywood experience on Facebook and Twitter.
•	Explore the park using the detailed map view.

NOTE: Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.
